                        <interp inst="t18801123-name-545" type="given" value="HENRY"></interp>HENRY GEORGE</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">Re-examined</hi>). The gateway is private—I pulled it to on the prisoner—the cart was my own.</p>
